First Union Corp said it hasagreed to acquire First State Bancshares Inc of Pensacola,Fla.,  and its First State Bank of Pensacola subsidiary forabout 457,000 common shares.    First State has assets of about 110 mln dlrs.  Theacquisition, expected to be treated as a pooling of interests,is expected to be completed in the third quarter of 1987subject to approval by regulatory agencies and First Stateshareholders. Reuter&#3;